data.description: 5 bedroom, 2 bath home with full basement perched upon 39+ acres in beautiful Calhan! Open floor plan features vaulted ceilings and is bursting with natural light from the windows and skylights. Very large kitchen with ample cabinet space and pantry, dining area with walk out access to the rear and the spacious living area includes a cozy fireplace. Private master bedroom with attached bath and walk in closet plus 3 additional bedrooms, full bath and laundry room on the main level. Downstairs, you'll find high ceilings, another large bedroom with a huge closet and plenty of room to use for a recreation room, family room, craft area; whatever you like! Bring all of your animals and toys and spread out on this beautiful property.
